dct_title_s: Map of Pennsylvania and New Jersey.
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures.   "Entered ... on the 20th day of August 1823, by H.S. Tanner, of the State of Pennsylvania."   "Engraved by H.S. Tanner and Assistants."   Includes (without detail)--contiguous portions of Connecticut, Massachusetts, New York, Upper Canada, Ohio, Virginia, Maryland, and Delaware.   Prime meridians: Washington (top)--and Greenwich (bottom).
